description: This header file declares functions related to sending reports over the RBUS communication method in a telemetry component. It includes function prototypes for sending reports and cached reports, and references external headers like telemetry2_0.h and vector.h.

methods.name: sendReportsOverRBUSMethod
methods.description: Sends telemetry reports over RBUS with specified method name, input parameters, and payload.

methods.name: sendCachedReportsOverRBUSMethod
methods.description: Sends cached telemetry reports over RBUS with specified method name, input parameters, and report list.
